{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just was getting very-- I-- I had no appetite whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to run in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave us a private bathroom for the-- for the orchestra for five people-- just us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the others were in the street, you know, all open up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was in my little bathroom-- and they were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- and there was heat in there and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I used to hide there every time it was lunchtime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Here people are dying from food they want to eat, and I have to disappear.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my sister said, if you don't eat, I'll kill you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then is when my brother came again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, why aren't you eating?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, I'm not hungry!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and I stay-- I said-- and then I started losing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, I didn't have the strength to go to the other concentration camp that we were going to go, because I was losing my strength.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So like this, I hardly ate up to when they took us away from there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So anyway, now things were coming to a close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw, one day, this happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- as we were in-- we were in the block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And suddenly, we hear-- we saw the German Nazis running here and there, and here and there, screaming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we found out that-- now this is the-- the sonnerkommander, they called it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the gas chambers, they have 40 people working for this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When people would come, they would-- they waited what they would do, put the people in the gas chambers and all that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then how they get out, whatever, I didn't want to know, really, but I know now.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
